Written by Bryan Henderson, San Jose California, December 2006.

13.11.08 Release 1.05

         Add ability to control the Curl timeout transport parameter.

13.08.15 Release 1.04

         Fix memory leak in Value::valueSimple() with arrays and structs.

12.03.11 Release 1.03

         Add Serialize.

07.01.13 Release 1.02

         Client::Curl::createObject():  Allow caller to specify all of the
         Curl transport parameters.

         Client::Curl::createObject():  Allow missing TRANSPORT_PARMS argument.

06.12.30 Release 1.01

         First release.
